Rating: 4
I gave this 4 stars because it's so easy. Nice change from mashed potatoes. Plus, it's versatile. You can add pretty much anything that might sound good. I added a bit of cinnamon, fresh shaved nutmeg, powdered ginger. Enhanced flavors nicely. served under pork tenderloin with balsamic/cranberry sauce. Flavors were delicious. Nice easy side dish.

