Very easy and delicious. A good way to use squash from the garden as a quick addition to dinner. I used chipotle pepper and did the bacon variation. Our dinner guests raved about it.

Rating: 4
I LOVE this recipe and make it all the time. Make sure you add the full amount of salt. Combined with the sweetness of the squash and the maple syrup, it elevates the taste to heavenly levels! I've used butternut, kabocha, and acorn squash, and each was delicious.

